ías","guid":"NzSQuFPEb501J5KNEsmoKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"312","parent":"274","text":"Onicogrifosis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"Descripción: Engrosamiento y curvatura anormal","guid":"ZgV8z09TQUgGn4wvETpX0A","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"Causas: Relacionado con la edad, posiblemente influenciado por endocrinopatías","guid":"Ke47OXxhWtsZg5laBdedAg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"315","parent":"0","text":"**Reumatología**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"- Coiloniquia: Forma de cuchara → Deficiencia de hierro/anemia","guid":"0CGSnL0lWRf381R1XIgV5w","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"315","text":"- Ranuras longitudinales: Líneas en uñas → Artritis reumatoide/envejecimiento","guid":"HvD60fk52dL5Y7E3COobqw","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"315","text":"- Uñas en mapa: Manchas irregulares → Vasculitis/autoinmunes","guid":"ZqC1oD5MML5gqM9QokKf5A","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"315","text":"- Onicorrexis: Uñas con grietas longitudinales → Artritis/envejecimiento","guid":"H637Pal9lqak1T7VxWV4Rg","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"0","text":"**Nefrología**","guid":"sP2wbCvMfgso9Qg1ayNgtg","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"- Uñas de Lindsay: Mitad y mitad → Insuficiencia renal crónica","guid":"YNzOM0zeL1Es_CMoB4VfPQ","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"320","text":"- Uñas de Muehrcke: Líneas blancas paralelas → Hipoproteinemia","guid":"g21mYfQ5AHL5wd6ySe7GRg","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"320","text":"- Uñas 'en dos tonos' o bicolor: Dos colores distintos → Alteraciones renales","guid":"twqmE4VOlDgtcukNrDCUOw","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"320","text":"- Lunares subungueales: Pigmentación oscura → Lesiones benignas/malignas en riñón","guid":"6USBA3K09SFkKB_xAoW4Dw","children":[]}]},{"id":"325","parent":"0","text":"**Oncología**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"326","parent":"325","text":"- Uñas de Hutchinson: Pigmentación oscura → Melanoma subungueal","guid":"co541